Adding a Subject:

Enter the name of the subject and select the deadline date.

Click "Add Subject" to add it to the list.

Deleting a Subject:

Click the trash icon (🗑️) next to a subject to remove it from the list.

Generating the Study Plan:

Enter the number of study hours you can dedicate per day.

Click "Generate Plan" to see your personalized study schedule.

Pomodoro Timer:

Click "Start" to begin a 25-minute Pomodoro session.

Click "Stop" to pause the timer.

Click "Reset" to reset the timer back to 25 minutes.

Saving the Plan:

Click "Save Plan" to save the generated study plan as a .txt file.
